# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SPECIFICATION OVERVIEW
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

## Purpose

The TB-HITL specification provides:
- **Requirements Traceability**: Full lineage from source documents to implementation
- **Business Rules**: Derived business logic with source citations
- **Acceptance Criteria**: Measurable verification criteria
- **Gap Analysis**: Implementation gaps and remediation plans

## Relationship to TB Spec

| Aspect | tb/ Spec | tb-hitl/ Spec |
|--------|----------|---------------|
| Focus | Technical design | Business requirements |
| Audience | Developers | Business owners, auditors |
| Traceability | Implementation | Source documents |
| Primary Use | Build reference | Compliance & audit |

## Key Documents

| Document | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `tb-hitl-spec.tex` | Main specification document |
| `chapters/04-business-requirements.tex` | Derived requirements |
| `chapters/14-traceability-matrix.tex` | Full traceability |
| `chapters/00-visual-traceability-map.tex` | Visual lineage |

